**Dame's Decision**: The album stays vaulted until three conditions are met: (1) Big 9's legal team confirms nothing on the album can be used against him, (2) Angel's Oakland situation is fully cold (no active federal interest), and (3) the Fountain Incident media cycle dies completely. Until then, it's locked in The Kennel's hard drive, encrypted, backed up on a USB in Dame's bra drawer next to Big 9's letters.

